        "image2_mask": "none",
        "subtitle": "",
        "title": "",
        "text": "<p>We are two friends from sunny Sarasota, Florida, bonded by a deep passion for open waters and a genuine appreciation for the freedom one experiences when riding a boat or jet ski. We love tinkering with our \"water toys\", always coming up with new product ideas to make our boating and riding experiences safer and more enjoyable.</p><p>It was during a 2019 brainstorming session, while developing a lighter, more compact, and efficient beach anchor, that we realized our innovations could benefit others and founded WavesRx.</p><p>So if you share the same passion for adventure and want to join us on this exhilarating journey, it would be a privilege to have you on-board!”</p>",
